        {
            "speaker": {
                "display_name": "Vivek Shankar",
                "matched_calendar_invitee_email": "vivek@growthxlabs.com"
            },
            "text": "So, you know, if we had a full month, I suppose we would have matched October, but generally we seem to have slowed down just a bit.",
